Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:47.78,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}友達にはもう戻れない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:55.70,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}恋人になれなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:10.74,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}昨日の夕暮れ偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:17.95,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}二人きり歩いた並木道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:47.78,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就算成不了戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:55.70,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也不再是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:10.74,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}昨天傍晚偶然與你相會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:17.95,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}兩人一起走過的林蔭道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  由綺也終於要成為偶像啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  所以…已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…冬彌…我…緒方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.89,0:00:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺  我聽不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.11,0:00:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這裏那麼吵…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單曲「Trisatto」創造了50萬張熱賣記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首張專輯「Darklist」也突破30萬張
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第六張單曲「Mac·the·Mac」首次突破100萬張
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在登上人氣頂峰之後的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.43,0:01:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.21,0:01:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自行創立緒方製作公司  並讓自己的妹妹理奈出道後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為經營者  又兼任著作曲  製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.01,0:01:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是走上新的道路的緒方英二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而由綺是繼理奈後  緒方製作公司培養的第二位藝人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由…綺…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.86,0:01:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為前輩的緒方理奈  經常和她說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.05,0:01:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  在一起的時候總是聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是會緊張的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊張？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是前輩  其實更像是老師一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會訓斥你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…是指緒方先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒方先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英二先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是理奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈的話倒不是像老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要說的話更像是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人經常在一起說笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  差不多到時間了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼最後能說一下今後的目標嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  已經中午了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種工作都想嘗試一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演戲也想試試
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是想像緒方理奈前輩一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力唱歌  希望能快點出唱片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天做客Fresh  eye的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現役女子大學生的森川由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是股票及外匯市場早報
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,截至今天上午收盤  平均股價比上周下跌了32.40日元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收於16804.15日元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國際外匯市場的日元匯率為1美元兌換163.65日元…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:05:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌君也來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺  剛才電視裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是錄影  你看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像個傻瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在主持人面前亂說對理奈的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  由綺  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為好像也是想讓我那樣回答的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就故意裝傻了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧  我很壞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺  要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  之後還有錄影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位是筱塚小姐  是我的經紀人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌君  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  總算是見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都帶著很重的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布朗寧詩集
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:32.21,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Robert  Browning：英國維多利亞時期的抒情詩人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅伯特·布朗寧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過定不下報告的主題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說想看看  令人心跳的戀愛詩歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩總是讓人沉醉於其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又充滿憂鬱…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道「哈梅倫的吹笛者」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:51.83,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈梅倫的吹笛者：布朗寧的作品之一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹笛男爵的那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之借你了  拿回去太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布朗寧是那個切斯特頓的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.69,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G·K·切斯特頓：英國短篇推理小說家 曾為布朗寧寫過文藝評論
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  那個「熱情的讀者」 你也看那個評傳了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的布朗神父探案集  有機會能借我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:14.00,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Father Brown 布朗神父是切斯特頓筆下的教士偵探
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…現在就借也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七瀨君說  她只要稍微有點時間就會來上課
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天見到由綺了嗎  美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  她不是沒事老是美笑  美笑的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是這樣  那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後會越來越忙  見面機會會更少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  不好好抓緊她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聽嗎  藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長說可以去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說店長…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從叔叔升級而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拒絕掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去做嗎…兼職的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真打算去做家庭教師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都來了為什麼不做  也已經登記過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去圖書館  你們兩個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  去還是不去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還要打工不是嗎  去工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人也沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,echoes的地址我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔…不  店長也不是不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟她一起去圖書館多好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經五年了啊  五年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也該下決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會以我的步調…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是借你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫個讀後感給美笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便我的那份報告也拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑可是借給你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧美笑  我才從差點輸給學分的危機中解脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了…今天的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天會借到這個  其實我是早就知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣無意識中繞了個彎子  做了那個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了睡過頭  打工被解雇  然後不得不來大學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是遇到了由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢和現實是連接著的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:11:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑其實是為了讓我和由綺見面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是完美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的推理如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花生君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰遜…啊  是哈德遜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種自認為越來越接近的想法真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  吹笛男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  今天的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌  要被聽到了哦  被另一個女神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌  去散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去  之後還要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,echoes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打網球的話我陪你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什麼叫哪壺不開提哪壺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙  等等  遙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意  彰那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到由綺了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是多虧了我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我不知道她還這麼在意她哥哥那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以後 她就再也沒有拿起過球拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是那麼被大家看好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全國大賽的名次也不差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒辦法啊  畢竟失去了最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法嗎  這麼放著她不管好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得  那傢伙好像在慢慢崩潰…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙一直都是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小時候開始就是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是還沒從打擊中恢復而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也用不著這麼生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改正
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我和由綺見面的女神似乎是遙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真羨慕你啊  周圍全是女神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺可不是女神哦  跟你說了很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也聽了很多次了  由綺是鄰家女孩對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可到今天你是幾個月沒見到那鄰家女孩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她剛剛搬到事務所準備的宿舍裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還沒裝好電話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地址呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被事務所那邊封口了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺真的成為偶像了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  …
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子竟然那麼老實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先  先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她們欺負了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們要你去買飲料嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:02.61,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺小姐  能幫買點飲料來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁機…但是為什麼  為什麼由綺要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:06.72,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要  我也要  我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那場面很難拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你不去買
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  當時我不在場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過目標是由綺的話  你在也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  是上周那件事的報復嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了吧  直接找我說不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她們是不會去找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有備用的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…不合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  該去下一個工作的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？要我幫你跟製作人說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧  理奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  我應該能解決的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  回來的時候我會再來看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別輸啊  由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:12.99,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,echoes咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  《密室推理》這月的來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是跟去圖書館比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說美笑的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《密室推理》的事啦  買不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:16:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般都是在圖書館看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我所以去不成了  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛才想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭奇  謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫了首不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那位是由綺那的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒方英二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由  由綺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在啦  怎麼可能在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼緒方英二會來這？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是…什麼時候來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長說  可以下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發今天的薪水了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼行  我們從上班到現在一個客人都沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能收
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  不  能  收
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你老爸看看如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就住附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我向那冷血動物低頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近大學的課程比較緊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工不太順利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想跟你談談…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒方理奈真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她一比  由綺真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  有請神田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:28.01,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅燈籠（居酒屋的俗稱）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都不正確
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼讓我們看看正確答案
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確答案…正確答案…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  就那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙眼  你真礙眼  快滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:43.06,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確答案是在家裏建了溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到由綺了啦  礙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡頭  笨蛋  你拍哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  誰啊  這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  藤井家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？由綺？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你不是在電視上…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是上周的錄影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  嚇到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收錄剛剛才完  因為早上沒能說上幾句話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  我當然在看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錄影也錄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可愛啊  非常可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比平常更…不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟平常一樣可愛  特別是見識了緒方理奈的可怕之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？她罵櫻團那些女孩的錄影放映了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為被剪掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  在那之後發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我也挺努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周會更有趣的  冬彌君一定要看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一定看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我從今天開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  在echoes嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懷念啊  那裏的手制芝士蛋糕很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個好像已經不賣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彰君的叔叔還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  店長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺  我今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我會再給你打電話的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.05,0:24:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二頁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.74,0:24:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就被安排好的相遇  你相信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.14,0:24:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White  Album

